SSI API ver. 0.1.0 1/13/2012

SsiDiskMarkAsSpare:
Function will return SSI_StatusFail instead of SSI_StatusInvalidState when called on a disk used by a RAID device.

SsiExpandVolume:
Function is implemented however this functionality depends on mdadm. During this release mdadm did not support such functionality.
Tested on mdadm 3.2.3. Future releases of mdadm may support this functionality.

SsiPhyLocate:
Currently this function is not supported.

